  /* VHX */
  .fullwidth {
  	max-width: 100%;
  }
  h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
  	font-family: 'Lato','Open Sans',sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .text-center { text-align: center; }
  .uppercase { text-transform: uppercase; }
  .hidden { display: none !important; }
  .padding-top { padding-top: 3em; }
  .padding-bottom { padding-bottom: 3em; }
  a, a:active {
  	color: #4e8793;
  }
  a:hover {
  	color: #d4a03f;
  }
  .section-title {
  	padding: 3em 0;
  }
  .section {
  	padding-bottom: 5em;
    position: relative;
  }
  .coloroverlay {
  	position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    opacity: .5;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  .dynamic-bg {
  	
  }
  .button {
  	display: inline-block;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    -webkit-border-radius: 4px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 300;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  
  .button:hover {
  	border: 2px solid #d4a03f;
    color: #000;
  }
  
  
  
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  /* HEADER */
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  nav {
  	border-bottom: 2px solid ;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 100;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #FFF;
  }
  nav h3 {
  	font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: inline;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  nav a,
  nav a:visited {
  	text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000;
  	padding: 10px;
    font-family: 'Lato',sans-serif;
    font-weight: 100;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  nav a:active,
  nav a:focus {
  	color: #000;
  }
  nav a:hover {
  	color: #000;
    background-color: #d4a03f;
  }
  nav.headroom {
    -webkit-transition: transform 200ms linear;
    -moz-transition: transform 200ms linear;
    -ms-transition: transform 200ms linear;
    -o-transition: transform 200ms linear;
    transition: transform 200ms linear;
  }
  nav.headroom--pinned {
    -webkit-transform: translateY(0%);
    -moz-transform: translateY(0%);
    -o-transform: translateY(0%);
    -ms-transform: translateY(0%);
    transform: translateY(0%);
  }
  nav.headroom--unpinned {
    -webkit-transform: translateY(-100%);
    -moz-transform: translateY(-100%);
    -o-transform: translateY(-100%);
    -ms-transform: translateY(-100%);
    transform: translateY(-100%);
  }
  @media only screen and (max-width: 40em) { 
  	nav a {
    	font-size: 12px;
    }
    nav h3 {
    	font-size: 12px;
      display: block;
    }
  }
  
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  /* NOTHING FOR SALE */
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  .intro {
  	padding-top: 5em;
  }
  
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  /* MAILING LIST */
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  .signup {
  	text-align: left;
  }
  .signup form {
  
  }
  .signup .form-title {
  	text-align: left;
    margin-left: 5px;
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  .signup input[type='email'] {
  	-webkit-appearance: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 13px 10px;
    font-family: 'Lato',sans-serif;
    font-weight: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #CCC;
  }
  .signup input[type='submit'] {
  	-webkit-appearance: none;
    border: 0px;
    background: transparent;
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 13px 15px;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    -webkit-border-radius: 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 300;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .signup input[type='submit']:hover {
  	border: 2px solid #d4a03f;
    color: #000;
  }
  .form.error input[type='submit'] {
  	border: 2px solid #f00;
  }
  .form.error input[type='email'] {
  	border-bottom: 1px solid #F00;
  }
  
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  /* TOP */
  /* - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - */
  .trailer {
  	position: relative;  
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .trailer .image {
  	background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center center;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
    opacity: 0;
    -webkit-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -moz-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -ms-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -o-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    transition: all .3s ease-in;
  }
  .trailer .image.is-active {
  	opacity: 1;
  }
  .trailer .image .coloroverlay {
  	position: absolute;
  }
  .trailer .image .overlay i {
  	position: relative;
  	top: 50%;
  	-webkit-transform: translateY(-50%);
  	-moz-transform: translateY(-50%);
  	-o-transform: translateY(-50%);
  	-ms-transform: translateY(-50%);
  	transform: translateY(-50%);
  }
  .trailer.padded {
  	padding: 80px 0 0 0;
  }
  .trailer .package-sharp {
  	position: relative;
    z-index: 20;
  	top: 80px;
  }
  .trailer .playback {
  	position: relative;
    -webkit-border-radius: 3px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    height: 0;
    padding-top: 56.25%;
  }
  .trailer .playback img {
  	-webkit-border-radius: 3px;
    border-radius: 3px;
     -webkit-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -moz-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -ms-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -o-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    transition: all .3s ease-in;
  }
  .bottomshadow:after {
  		content: "";
      width: 98%;
      height: 1px;
      bottom: 0px;
      left: 1%;
      display: block;
      position: absolute;
      z-index: -1;
  
      -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 8px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
         -moz-box-shadow: 0px 0px 8px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
              box-shadow: 0px 0px 8px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  }
  
  .trailer .playback a {
  	position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
     -webkit-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -moz-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -ms-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -o-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    transition: all .3s ease-in;
    overflow: hidden;
    -webkit-border-radius: 3px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .trailer .playback a .overlay {
  	opacity: 0;
  	position: absolute;
  	top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 10;
     -webkit-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -moz-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -ms-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    -o-transition: all .3s ease-in;
    transition: all .3s ease-in;
    background-color: #4e8793;
  }
  .trailer .playback i {
  	position: absolute;
  	top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 12;
    color: #FFF;
    opacity: 0;
    -webkit-transition: all .3s ease-in;

          // very rudimentary email checking
          if (!email){
            $(this).addClass("error");
            $(this).find('input[type="email"]').attr("placeholder","Enter a valid email");
          } else {
            var at_location = email.indexOf("@");
            var dot_location = email.indexOf(".",at_location);
